name: Ella Print 8"x10"
description:
Ella is a sultry little vixen deciding which heart to grab next. I think you’ll agree that she has a magnificent dress! I wish I could squeeze into it, but I doubt she’d lend it to me anyway.

	This is a 8.5” x 11” digital print of my original pencil and charcoal illustration. She was one of my ‘holiday series’ of cheeky girls.

	She comes signed and dated on the back (or the front if you prefer – just let me know).

name: Poppy Print 8" x 10"
description:
Poppy is a natural flirt. She’s surrounded by poppies blowing in the breeze and is wearing a sweet little headband with a poppy brooch attached to it.

	And her off-the-shoulder blue dress is sure to attract the attention of that gorgeous young man she’s just spotted!

	This is an 8” x 10” digital print of my original coloured-pencil illustration. It has a generous white border to make framing easier and it comes signed and dated.

name: Grace Print 8"x10"
description:
Grace is a new look for me. The original piece is going to be my main entry in the Linden Gallery Postcard Show in Melbourne.

	I’m besotted with the soft green in her eyes and I really love having all the focus on her face and decollatage. It’s a departure from my usual bright style, but there’s sopmething mesmerising about this piece. You don’t get all the detail in one glance, so it retains a little mystery!

	This 8”x10” digital print of Grace is signed and dated on the back and comes carefully packed in a protective sleeve.

	It also has a generous white border (in fact the entire piece is A3 in size) so there’s plenty of room for framing.
